  <title>Slider</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword>Definition<keyword>Slider</keyword></keyword>
    <keyword>Motion-Part<keyword>Slider</keyword></keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><table styleclass="PopupTable" rowcount="1" colcount="2" style="width:450px;">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:174px;">
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><image src="Kin-Slider.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"><caption><![CDATA[Slider]]></caption></image></para>
        </td>
        <td style="width:266px;">
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">A <text styleclass="Popup Box2">Slider</text> is a <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Part</text> that is:</para>
          <list id="2" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="Popup Box">joined to another <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Part</text> with a <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Slide-Joint" styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Slide-Joint</link>&#32;</li>
            <li styleclass="Popup Box">its position is specified by a <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Motion-Dimension-FB" styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Motion-Dimension FB</link><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">. </text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">It is also a :</para>
          <list id="3" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="Popup Box"><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Motion-Driven-Part" styleclass="Popup Box2">Motion-Part</link>, </li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted - compressed" style="margin-top:0px;"><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Part-Kinematically-Defined" styleclass="VariableName-small">kinematically-defined Part</link> (<text styleclass="VariableName-small">Solved Part</text>)</li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">Its motion may be stationary, reciprocating, or sliding with a constant or varying linear velocity.</para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="SeeAlso-small">See also: <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Rocker">Rocker</link>, <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dyad">Dyads</link></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
